---
import Button from "../ui/Button.astro";
import SectionImage from "../../assets/images/home/proyects/1.jpg";

const span = "font-bold text-neutral-900";
---

<section
  class="py-16 lg:py-20 2xl:py-24 lg:flex lg:px-5 lg:justify-center relative bg-subtle-radial"
>
  <div
    class="h-full w-full lg:max-w-[55rem] xl:max-w-[68rem] 2xl:max-w-[76rem] xl:gap-6 flex justify-center items-center lg:flex"
  >
    <div
      class="h-full flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start justify-center gap-7 md:gap-9 lg:gap-5 xl:gap-7 2xl:gap-9 px-5 xl:px-0 lg:w-full"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] font-oswald text-accent-600 uppercase">Sobre Sitec</span>
        <h1
          class="font-oswald text-3xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl 2xl:text-[2.6rem] text-primary-600 leading-tight max-w-[18ch] text-center lg:text-start"
        >
          Energía que Inspira Confianza
        </h1>
        <span class="block h-[3px] w-14 rounded-full bg-accent-500/70 mt-1"></span>
      </div>

      <p
        class="text-center lg:text-start text-sm lg:text-sm xl:text-[0.95rem] 2xl:text-base leading-[1.75rem] lg:leading-[1.65rem] xl:leading-[1.8rem] 2xl:leading-[1.9rem] md:max-w-[80ch] xl:max-w-[60ch] 2xl:max-w-[62ch] text-neutral-600"
      >
        En <span class={span}>SITEC</span> ofrecemos soluciones eléctricas integrales
        a medida. Nos encargamos de la planificación y ejecución de proyectos eléctricos
        y electromecánicos, priorizando <span class={span}>eficiencia</span>, <span
          class={span}>seguridad</span
        > y <span class={span}>cumplimiento normativo.</span>
        <br />
        <br /> Con un equipo experimentado y tecnología de vanguardia, garantizamos
        instalaciones confiables y resultados que superan expectativas.
      </p>

      <div class="lg:mt-2">
        <Button href="/about-us" variant="outline">VER MÁS</Button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hidden lg:flex w-[40rem] xl:w-[57rem] h-full items-center">
      <div class="relative w-full flex items-center justify-end">
        <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-[70%] h-[80%] rounded-3xl bg-primary-50 -z-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 right-12 w-24 h-24 rounded-2xl bg-accent-100 -z-10"></div>
        <img
          src={SectionImage.src}
          class="h-[22rem] xl:h-[26rem] 2xl:h-[28rem] w-[82%] xl:w-[78%] 2xl:w-[80%] rounded-3xl object-cover shadow-elevated ring-1 ring-primary-100/70"
          alt="Proyecto Sitec"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
